他交给你们了
He's all yours.

1056
01:19:24,590 --> 01:19:26,400
那是什么玩意  我们准许去那里了吗
What the hell was that? Were we cleared to go in there?

1057
01:19:25,570 --> 01:19:28,870
{\an8}{\pos(186,190)}加州  爱德华兹空军基地

1058
01:19:26,400 --> 01:19:27,620
没有  长官  他们用了人肉盾
No, sir, they were using human shields.

1059
01:19:27,620 --> 01:19:28,740
我们没获得批准
We never got the green light.

1060
01:19:28,740 --> 01:19:30,350
给我接国务院  肯定是他们搞的
Put me through to State. They're going to be all over this.

1061
01:19:30,350 --> 01:19:31,890
调出显示
Get those monitors up!

1062
01:19:32,380 --> 01:19:33,370
发现不明物体
We got a bogey!

1063
01:19:33,690 --> 01:19:35,950
-不是空军  -接通中情局了吗
- Wasn't Air Force! - We got the CIA on the line?

1064
01:19:35,950 --> 01:19:38,080
我接通了兰利  他们还问是不是我们
I've got Langley on the line. They want to know if it's us.

1065
01:19:38,080 --> 01:19:39,710
绝对不是我们  长官
No, it definitely is not us, sir!

1066
01:19:39,710 --> 01:19:41,470
-不是海军  -不是陆战队
- It wasn't Navy. - Wasn't Marines.

1067
01:19:41,480 --> 01:19:44,300
我需要答案  能拿到目标图像吗
I need answers! Can I please get eyes on target?

1068
01:19:44,300 --> 01:19:46,400
-不能  -无法识别
- Negative, negative. - Cannot identify.

1069
01:19:46,400 --> 01:19:49,090
马上把武器研发的罗德中校叫来
Get me Colonel Rhodes from Weapons Development down here now!

1070
01:19:55,880 --> 01:19:56,750
我们查了身份
We ran an ID check

1071
01:19:56,750 --> 01:19:58,770
并交叉对比了所有已知数据库
and cross-referenced with all known databases.

1072
01:19:58,770 --> 01:19:59,580
毫无发现
We have nothing.

1073
01:19:59,580 --> 01:20:01,730
当地有高空监控吗
Any high altitude surveillance in the region?

1074
01:20:01,730 --> 01:20:03,550
当地有空中早期预警和全球鹰
We got an AWAC and a Global Hawk in the area.

1075
01:20:03,550 --> 01:20:05,230
这玩意是突然冒出来的吗
So this thing just appeared out of nowhere?

1076
01:20:05,230 --> 01:20:06,800
怎么会没在雷达上发现
How come it didn't show up on the radar?

1077
01:20:06,800 --> 01:20:08,790
只有很小的雷达截面  长官
Got a minimal radar cross-section, sir.

1078
01:20:08,790 --> 01:20:11,130
-隐形的吗  -不是  长官  它很小
- Is it stealth? - No, sir, it's tiny.

1079
01:20:11,140 --> 01:20:13,190
应该是无人机
We think it's an unmanned aerial vehicle.

1080
01:20:13,500 --> 01:20:15,300
中校  这是什么情况
Colonel, what are we dealing with here?

1081
01:20:17,940 --> 01:20:20,430
-我去打个电话  -中士  清条线路
- Let me make a call. - Sergeant, clear a hole.

1082
01:20:24,510 --> 01:20:26,330
-喂  -托尼
- Hello? - Tony?

1083
01:20:26,330 --> 01:20:28,220
-谁啊  -罗德
- Who's this? - It's Rhodes.

1084
01:20:28,340 --> 01:20:30,480
-抱歉  谁  -我说是罗德
- Sorry, hello? - I said it's Rhodes.

1085
01:20:30,490 --> 01:20:33,200
-请大点声  -那是什么噪音
- Speak up, please. - What in the hell is that noise?

1086
01:20:33,400 --> 01:20:35,070
嗯  我敞篷开车呢
Oh, yeah, I'm driving with the top down.

1087
01:20:35,140 --> 01:20:36,960
我现在需要你帮忙
Yeah, well, I need your help right now.

1088
01:20:36,960 --> 01:20:38,320
天道好轮回啊
It's funny how that works, huh?

1089
01:20:38,320 --> 01:20:39,420
是啊  是这样
Yeah. Speaking of funny,

1090
01:20:39,420 --> 01:20:41,770
有个武器站刚被炸毁了
we've got a weapons depot that was just blown up

1091
01:20:41,770 --> 01:20:43,610
离你当初被囚的地方只有几公里
a few clicks from where you were being held captive.

1092
01:20:43,610 --> 01:20:45,380
那里挺危险的
Well, that's a hot spot.

1093
01:20:45,380 --> 01:20:47,820
似乎是有人插手替你完成了工作  是吧
Sounds like someone stepped in and did your job for you, huh?

1094
01:20:47,820 --> 01:20:49,080
你为什么气喘吁吁的  托尼
Why do you sound out of breath, Tony?

1095
01:20:49,080 --> 01:20:50,330
我没有  我在峡谷里慢跑呢
I'm not, I was justjogging in the canyon.

1096
01:20:50,330 --> 01:20:52,230
-你不是在开车吗  -是啊  我开车
- I thought you were driving. - Right, I was driving

1097
01:20:52,230 --> 01:20:54,030
到了峡谷  然后去慢跑
to the canyon, where I'm going to jog.

1098
01:20:54,030 --> 01:20:55,230
你在那一带真没有什么
You sure you don't have any tech

1099
01:20:55,230 --> 01:20:56,610
我应该知道的东西吗
in that area I should know about?

1100
01:20:56,620 --> 01:20:58,240
-没有  -发现不明物体了
- Nope! - Bogey spotted!

1101
01:20:58,240 --> 01:20:59,570
鞭子战机  正在前往
Whiplash, come in hot.

1102
01:20:59,570 --> 01:21:01,450
很好  因为我眼前就有个东西
Okay, good, 'cause I'm staring at one right now,

1103
01:21:01,450 --> 01:21:03,500
马上要被炸飞了
and it's about to be blown to kingdom come.

1104
01:21:04,740 --> 01:21:05,980
我该撤了
That's my exit.

1105
01:21:11,500 --> 01:21:12,830
战情室  这里是鞭子一号
Ballroom, this is Whiplash One.

1106
01:21:12,830 --> 01:21:14,530
我看到不明物体了
I've got the bogey in my sights.

1107
01:21:15,100 --> 01:21:16,730
鞭子一号  那是什么玩意
Whiplash One, what is it?

1108
01:21:16,730 --> 01:21:18,110
我不知道
I've got no idea.

1109
01:21:18,110 --> 01:21:20,570
-能进行无线电联络吗  -无反应  长官
- You have radio contact? - Non responsive, sir.

1110
01:21:20,570 --> 01:21:22,200
那你可以交火
Then you are clear to engage.

1111
01:21:23,430 --> 01:21:24,560
{\an8}超音速飞行

1112
01:21:23,690 --> 01:21:24,690
启动
Hit it.

1113
01:21:29,520 --> 01:21:31,910
不明物体刚进入了超音速  我锁定了
That bogey just went supersonic. I got a lock!

1114
01:21:36,500 --> 01:21:39,070
-导弹来袭  -照明弹
- lnbound missile. - Flares!

1115
01:21:41,530 --> 01:21:43,500
等等  不明物体调用了照明弹
Wait a second. Bogey deployed flares!

1116
01:21:58,490 --> 01:21:59,560
展开襟翼
Deploy flaps!

1117
01:22:00,980 --> 01:22:01,910
我去
Holy!

1118
01:22:02,220 --> 01:22:03,780
那玩意从雷达上消失了  长官
That thing just jumped off the radar, sir.

1119
01:22:03,790 --> 01:22:05,430
卫星盯丢了
The sat visual has been lost.

1120
01:22:05,540 --> 01:22:07,290
那绝不是无人机
No way that's a UAV.

1121
01:22:07,350 --> 01:22:08,370
是什么
What is it?

1122
01:22:08,370 --> 01:22:09,800
我什么都看不到
I can't see anything.

1123
01:22:10,080 --> 01:22:12,300
不管是什么  刚刚已经死了
Whatever it was, it just bought the farm.

1124
01:22:13,080 --> 01:22:15,010
不明物体应该已经被处理掉了  长官
I think bogey's been handled, sir.

1125
01:22:25,060 --> 01:22:26,840
-喂  -罗德  是我
- Hello? - Hi, Rhodey, it's me.

1126
01:22:26,840 --> 01:22:28,670
-谁  -抱歉  确实是我
- It's who? - I'm sorry, it is me.

1127
01:22:28,670 --> 01:22:30,010
你问了  你问的那个就是我
You asked. What you were asking about is me.

1128
01:22:30,010 --> 01:22:31,600
瞧  这不是游戏
No, see, this isn't a game.

1129
01:22:31,600 --> 01:22:34,840
你不能把平民装备飞入我的活动战区
You do not send civilian equipment into my active war zone.

1130
01:22:34,840 --> 01:22:37,060
-你懂不懂  -不是一件装备
- You understand that? - This is not a piece of equipment.

1131
01:22:37,060 --> 01:22:39,700
我在里面呢  是件战衣  那是我
I'm in it. It's a suit. It's me!

1132
01:22:39,850 --> 01:22:41,460
罗德  你查到什么了吗
Rhodey, you got anything for me?

1133
01:22:43,330 --> 01:22:46,270
-标记位置  回基地  -收到  战情室
- Mark your position and return to base. - Roger that, Ballroom.

1134
01:22:49,040 --> 01:22:50,110
在你底下
On your belly!

1135
01:22:50,110 --> 01:22:52,210
像是个人
lt looks like a man!

1136
01:22:52,350 --> 01:22:54,910
甩掉他  翻滚
Shake him off! Roll! Roll!

1137
01:23:03,020 --> 01:23:04,470
我被打中了
I'm hit! I'm hit!

1138
01:23:04,470 --> 01:23:06,120
确认  他被击中了
It's confirmed. He has been hit.

1139
01:23:10,720 --> 01:23:12,300
跳伞
Punch out! Punch out!

1140
01:23:19,180 --> 01:23:20,880
鞭子一号坠机
Whiplash One down.

1141
01:23:21,050 --> 01:23:22,700
鞭子二号  看到降落伞了吗
Whiplash Two, do you see a chute?

1142
01:23:22,700 --> 01:23:24,970
没有  没有降落伞
Negative! No chute, no chute!

1143
01:23:30,520 --> 01:23:31,930
我的降落伞卡住了
My chute's jammed!

1144
01:23:37,760 --> 01:23:40,030
长官  我看到不明物体了
Sir, I've got a visual on the bogey.

1145
01:23:40,230 --> 01:23:41,430
鞭子二号  再次出击
Whiplash Two, reengage.

1146
01:23:41,430 --> 01:23:43,250
如果能击落  就击落
If you get a clear shot, you take it.

1147
01:23:45,420 --> 01:23:47,180
少校  我们都不知道那是什么
Major, we don't even know what we're shooting at.

1148
01:23:47,180 --> 01:23:47,840
让猛禽回来
Call off the Raptors.

1149
01:23:47,850 --> 01:23:49,230
那玩意刚在合法禁飞区内
That thing just took out an F- 22

1150
01:23:49,230 --> 01:23:50,680
击落了一架F22
inside a legal no fly zone!

1151
01:23:50,680 --> 01:23:53,370
鞭子二号  如果能击落  就击落
Whiplash Two, if you have a clear shot, take it!

1152
01:23:53,370 --> 01:23:55,830
你又被锁定了  进行躲避操作
You've been reengaged. Execute evasive manoeuvre.

1153
01:23:55,830 --> 01:23:56,760
继续飞
Keep going!

1154
01:24:04,730 --> 01:24:06,790
降落伞打开
Good chute! Good chute!

1155
01:24:14,420 --> 01:24:17,260
-托尼  你还在吗  -谢谢了
- Tony, you still there? - Hey, thanks.

1156
01:24:17,260 --> 01:24:19,870
天呐  你个疯子
Oh, my God, you crazy son of a bitch.

1157
01:24:20,690 --> 01:24:22,660
你欠我架飞机  你知道吧
You owe me a plane. You know that, right?

1158
01:24:23,950 --> 01:24:25,740
严格讲  是他撞了我
Yeah, well, technically, he hit me.

1159
01:24:25,740 --> 01:24:27,710
你要过来看看我在做什么吗
Now are you going to come by and see what I'm working on?

1160
01:24:27,710 --> 01:24:30,860
不要  我知道得越少越好
No, no, no, no, no, no, the less I know, the better.

1161
01:24:31,160 --> 01:24:32,820
我要怎么跟媒体讲
Now, what am I supposed to tell the press?

1162
01:24:32,820 --> 01:24:35,400
演练  一般不都用这套屁话吗
Training exercise. Isn't that the usual BS?

1163
01:24:35,410 --> 01:24:36,860
没那么简单
It's not that simple.

1164
01:24:37,960 --> 01:24:39,870
昨天一架猛禽F22
An unfortunate training exercise

1165
01:24:39,870 --> 01:24:42,980
在演练中不幸发生事故
involving an F-22 Raptor occurred yesterday.

1166
01:24:43,460 --> 01:24:46,720
庆幸的是  飞行员并未受伤
I am pleased to report that the pilot was not injured.

1167
01:24:46,950 --> 01:24:50,700
至于科米拉村庄意料之外的局势反转
As for the unexpected turn of events on the ground in Gulmira,

1168
01:24:50,940 --> 01:24:54,560
是谁或是什么进行了干预  我们尚不清楚
it is still unclear who or what intervened,

1169
01:24:54,560 --> 01:24:55,830
但我可以保证
but I can assure you that

1170
01:24:55,830 --> 01:24:58,800
此事与美国政府无关
the United States government was not involved.

1171
01:25:03,750 --> 01:25:05,450
的确很贴身  先生
It is a tight fit, sir.

1172
01:25:06,630 --> 01:25:09,480
先生  您越是扭动  就会越疼
Sir, the more you struggle, the more this is going to hurt.

1173
01:25:09,580 --> 01:25:11,220
温柔点  这是我第一次
Be gentle. This is my first time.

1174
01:25:12,450 --> 01:25:14,410
我设计它能脱下来的  所以
I designed this to come off, so...

1175
01:25:16,580 --> 01:25:17,910
我真的应该能
I really should be able to...

1176
01:25:18,860 --> 01:25:20,480
请尽量不要动  先生
Please, try not to move, sir.

1177
01:25:21,800 --> 01:25:23,220
怎么回事啊
What's going on here?

1178
01:25:28,640 --> 01:25:29,290
承认吧
Let's face it.

1179
01:25:29,290 --> 01:25:31,340
这不是你撞见我做的最糟糕的事
This is not the worst thing you've caught me doing.

1180
01:25:33,290 --> 01:25:34,850
那是弹孔吗
Are those bullet holes?

1181
01:26:02,670 --> 01:26:03,650
欢迎
Welcome.

1182
01:26:07,220 --> 01:26:09,050
托尼·斯塔克的赠礼
Compliments of Tony Stark.

1183
01:26:10,260 --> 01:26:11,860
如果你当初按计划杀了他
If you'd killed him when you were supposed to,

1184
01:26:11,860 --> 01:26:13,460
也不会把脸烧掉了
you'd still have a face.

1185
01:26:13,960 --> 01:26:16,160
你给我们点小钱杀一位王子
You paid us trinkets to kill a prince.

1186
01:26:16,210 --> 01:26:17,760
带我去看武器
Show me the weapon.

1187
01:26:19,170 --> 01:26:22,770
来吧  让守卫留在外面
Come. Leave your guards outside.

1188
01:26:39,470 --> 01:26:41,680
