His escape bore unexpected fruit.

1189
01:26:44,640 --> 01:26:46,490
他就是这么做到的
So this is how he did it.

1190
01:26:46,930 --> 01:26:49,000
这只是首次的粗糙的尝试
This is only a first, crude effort.

1191
01:26:49,460 --> 01:26:51,850
斯塔克已完善了他的设计
Stark has perfected his design.

1192
01:26:52,310 --> 01:26:55,050
他制作了一件死亡杰作
He has made a masterpiece of death.

1193
01:26:55,430 --> 01:26:58,670
有十几件这种战衣的人  能统治亚洲
A man with a dozen of these can rule all of Asia.

1194
01:27:00,310 --> 01:27:02,410
你梦想夺下斯塔克的王位
And you dream of Stark's throne.

1195
01:27:04,420 --> 01:27:06,090
我们有共同的敌人
We have a common enemy.

1196
01:27:10,960 --> 01:27:12,450
如果我们还在合作
If we are still in business,

1197
01:27:15,470 --> 01:27:17,530
我会把设计给你
I will give you these designs

1198
01:27:19,230 --> 01:27:20,290
当做礼物
as a gift.

1199
01:27:21,870 --> 01:27:22,960
作为交换
And in turn,

1200
01:27:24,920 --> 01:27:26,630
希望你能礼尚往来
I hope you'll repay me

1201
01:27:27,850 --> 01:27:30,420
给我钢铁战士
with a gift of iron soldiers.

1202
01:27:41,050 --> 01:27:43,920
这是你唯一会得到的礼物
This is the only gift you shall receive.

1203
01:27:46,990 --> 01:27:48,210
科技
Technology.

1204
01:27:50,240 --> 01:27:53,320
在世界的这一带一直是个致命弱点
It's always been your Achilles' heel in this part of the world.

1205
01:27:55,000 --> 01:27:58,470
别担心  只会持续15分钟
Don't worry. It'll only last for 1 5 minutes.

1206
01:27:59,310 --> 01:28:01,300
这是你最不需要担心的事了
That's the least of your problems.

1207
01:28:06,950 --> 01:28:09,250
把装甲和其余的装箱带走
Crate up the armour and the rest of it.

1208
01:28:11,240 --> 01:28:13,180
好  我们做个了结吧
All right, let's finish up here.

1209
01:28:17,250 --> 01:28:20,210
让方舟反应堆下的16区做好准备
Set up Sector 16 underneath the arc reactor,

1210
01:28:20,210 --> 01:28:22,280
我需要遮蔽这些数据
and I'm going to want this data masked.

1211
01:28:22,280 --> 01:28:23,970
找来我们最好的工程师
Recruit our top engineers.

1212
01:28:23,970 --> 01:28:25,790
马上给我造个原型机
I want a prototype right away.

1213
01:28:35,070 --> 01:28:36,940
你忙吗  可以替我去办件事吗
You busy? You mind if I send you on an errand?

1214
01:28:37,180 --> 01:28:39,220
我需要你去我办公室
I need you to go to my office.

1215
01:28:39,880 --> 01:28:41,080
黑入主机
You're going to hack into the mainframe

1216
01:28:41,090 --> 01:28:42,970
拿到所有最近的运输清单
and you're going to retrieve all the recent shipping manifests.

1217
01:28:42,970 --> 01:28:44,480
这是锁定芯片
This is a lock chip.

1218
01:28:45,140 --> 01:28:46,430
能让你黑进去
This'll get you in.

1219
01:28:46,830 --> 01:28:48,470
大概是在执行文档里
It's probably under Executive Files.

1220
01:28:48,470 --> 01:28:50,300
要不  就是在幽灵驱动上
If not, they put it on a ghost drive,

1221
01:28:50,300 --> 01:28:52,920
那样的话  你就得查找标题数码最小的
